  "key": "A# major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 7,
  "lyrics": "Is it too much for me to hate? For you to hear me? Is it too much when I go and ask you things? Is there no intent for this? No want for this? Is there nothing that sets your light on fire? The day you let me come Try to sweep you off the land Holding on to win, times matter more Holding on to win, life didn't make you Hug me, hold and cry Take all the things away from your baby Even when I know This is probably not what you wanna do I'm probably not who you wanna see But just think, what if it was? You never know where you go Never know what you do If you don't take the jump Take the chance and run along with me In your mind I know you think about me sometimes Think about me In a way that makes you doubt me I know you'll probably tell me to go But hold the thought for a second Breathe a night that you'll reckon Maybe hold, maybe lie Hold the light next to your heart Lie next to your heart Hold the light above me As you tell me no But baby, if you say then one day you'll know Maybe next year, next year, next year, next year Light, your friend",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 14.960000038146973,
      "text": "Is it too much for me to hate? For you to hear me?",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 21.3799991607666,
      "text": "Is it too much when I go and ask you things?",
      "start": 16
    },
    {
      "end": 26.360000610351562,
      "text": "Is there no intent for this? No want for this?",
      "start": 22.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 31.360000610351562,
      "text": "Is there nothing that sets your light on fire?",
      "start": 26.360000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 44.459999084472656,
      "text": "The day you let me come Try to sweep you off the land",
      "start": 33.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 51.97999954223633,
      "text": "Holding on to win, times matter more Holding on to win, life didn't make you",
      "start": 44.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 58.880001068115234,
      "text": "Hug me, hold and cry Take all the things away from your baby",
      "start": 51.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 65.66000366210938,
      "text": "Even when I know This is probably not what you wanna do",
      "start": 58.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 74.95999908447266,
      "text": "I'm probably not who you wanna see But just think, what if it was?",
      "start": 65.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 83.87999725341797,
      "text": "You never know where you go Never know what you do",
      "start": 75.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 91.87999725341797,
      "text": "If you don't take the jump Take the chance and run along with me",
      "start": 83.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 97.63999938964844,
      "text": "In your mind I know you think about me sometimes",
      "start": 91.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 104.83999633789062,
      "text": "Think about me In a way that makes you doubt me",
      "start": 97.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 115.83999633789062,
      "text": "I know you'll probably tell me to go But hold the thought for a second",
      "start": 106.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 123.87999725341797,
      "text": "Breathe a night that you'll reckon Maybe hold, maybe lie",
      "start": 116.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 132.8800048828125,
      "text": "Hold the light next to your heart Lie next to your heart",
      "start": 125.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 143.6199951171875,
      "text": "Hold the light above me As you tell me no",
      "start": 135.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 147.89999389648438,
      "text": "But baby, if you say then one day you'll know",
      "start": 143.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 150.8800048828125,
      "text": "Maybe next year, next year, next year, next year",
      "start": 147.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 152.44000244140625,
      "text": "Light, your friend",
      "start": 151.6999969482422
    }
